{"comment": ["(12oz bottle) AROMA: light malt nose, hint of soft/swelet grain, minimal hops, wet paper, toich of biscuit, basic bland lager nose APPEARANCE: very clear, straw yellow, light head TASTE: some grain, some sweetness, touch of hops, strightforwrd beer PALATE: very crisp, clean, a tad creamy, some midde bitterness but not much followthru, recreshing OVERALL: an ok lager, better than the Amercian mass lagers, a bit more 'beer' than those but still an easy and refreshing beer, basically a moderate amount of lager-ness and almost no negative aspects (other than being kinda light).  ", "Aroma: Wet Hay\r\nFlavor: Watery yeasty\r\nBitterness: Restrained\r\nColour: Light Gold\r\nVisual Carbonation: Fast Rising Bubbles\r\nClarity: Clear\r\nHead Retention: Low Thin White Head\r\nLacing: Very little\r\nBody: Soft\r\nPalate: Mild almost non existant hops\r\nFinish: Short\r\nAlcohol: Not Detectable\r\n ", " Birra commerciale pi\u00f9 conosciuta in Europa . A me non mi piace tanto e non dice gran che, ma  non concordo con quelle recensioni che dicono che faccia schifo. ", " (pour l'enfant que j'ai \u00e9t\u00e9 (attention : ce genre de bi\u00e8re a tellement corrompu notre soci\u00e9t\u00e9 (et moi-m\u00eame \u00e9tant jeune) que je me jure de ne plus en boire)) ", "at least I don't drink cider lolxzxzxzxzxzxzxz\r\nadd my gamertag xXxXBeErLuVeR2002xXxx ", " Une des pires bi\u00e8res \u00e0 mes yeux \nPas de go\u00fbts ou tr\u00e8s mauvais. \nElle est vendue par pack de 100 \u00e0 plus savoir quoi en faire comme certaine marque proche ... \u00c9ventuellement se rabattre sur les version pression pour sauver la mise  ", " 500ml Draught: Pours a crystal clear golden with thin white head. Aroma of hay, cracker and some bready notes as well. Flavors are cereal, bread with slight corn notes. Beer is slightly sweet with low bitterness. Body is light and carbonation is medium. Overall a good thirst quencher and as lager goes, not too bad. ", "Can at home. Straight out of the can. Doesn't have much going on, just an average pale lager. I'm sure it didn't see any hops in its lifetime. Lucky no corn either.  ", "Barwa jasno s\u0142omkowa. Piana \u015brednioobfita, \u015bredniop\u0119cherzykowa, szybko opada do zera.\r\nAromat: skunks, skunks, skuns. Lekka s\u0142odowo\u015b\u0107.\r\nW smaku to co w aromacie. Delikatna goryczka. Wodnisty jak typowy eurolager. ", "650ml bottle. Pours a light straw with white head. Large lager nose. Light body with clear lager flavours and little else.  "], "beer_name": "Heineken", "user": ["Rex_Remes", "Haleale", "gladiator7", "julesxxl", "beerluvr2002", "seanfr", "AntonyWilson", "Scrumpy369", "karolsks", "Samtzu"], "nr_reviews": ["287", "29", "8", "496", "3", "19", "515", "991", "63", "641"], "score": "2.5 out of 5.0<br /><small>Aroma 4/10<br />Appearance 2/5<br />Taste 5/10<br />Palate 3/5<br />Overall 11/20<br /></small"}
