{"comment": ["On tap at The Woolpack Inn, Leicester on 04-Feb-2017. Clear light pale amber with a medium sized white head. Aroma of sweet malt, grain and bread, Light to medium body and heavily carbonated. Taste of grain and sweet breads. Light bitterness. Pretty boring commercial lager. ", "Slight herbal aroma, pours golden. Very thin mouth feel, slightly sweet aftertaste, nothing much going on really.  ", "11.2 oz. bottle. Pour was clear golden, large white head. Aroma was grassy, green vegetables. Taste was light bitterness, grassy. ", "Butelka. Aromat s\u0142odowy, lekko utlenione, lagerowe. W smaku jak lager, nic specjalnego, goryczka bardzo niska.  ", "Bottle.Clear pale straw,thick,not very beautiful but quite stable white head,some lacing.Aroma malty,slight dms,weak cardboard.Taste sweetish,malty.Carbonation medium.Bitterness very low.Aftertaste malty,cardboard,corn.Weak and boring. ", "Backlog. Przenoszenie ocen z innego serwisu, z czas\u00f3w przed za\u0142o\u017ceniem konta na ratebeer ", "Pours gold with a thick white head strong malt aroma not a whole lot of flavor which is probably good more drinkable that way. Bottle from World Of Beers Middleton Wi  ", "Bi\u00e8re de tr\u00e8s grande distribution. Aucune autre vertu que la d\u00e9salt\u00e9ration. ", "Can on a Delta flight from Paris to Seattle. Clear golden color with white head. Aroma is grainy, bready, with some malt sweetness. Taste is sweet malts, bready, . Silky mouthfeel with medium to high soft carbonation. Drinkable. ", "Piwo barwy z\u0142otej, piana \u015brednio obfita, lecz bardzo nietrwa\u0142a. W aromacie s\u0142odowa s\u0142odycz. W smaku dziwne, nieco s\u0142odowe, lecz do\u015b\u0107 wytrawne i kwaskowate. Og\u00f3lnie jest kiepsko, a nawet bardzo kiepsko. Nie polecam. "], "beer_name": "Kronenbourg 1664", "user": ["R4N5H", "aholmes987", "ozzy70", "kacyper", "weaver23ph", "jandorris", "Mindwarp", "alrick", "SinH4", "micia600"], "nr_reviews": ["1384", "23", "1357", "1497", "431", "947", 